trans-unit.source: Used by the <xref href="System.Web.SiteMap"></xref> class to track the set of <xref href="System.Web.SiteMapProvider"></xref> objects that are available to the <xref href="System.Web.SiteMap"></xref> during site map initialization.
trans-unit.target: Utilizado pelo <xref href="System.Web.SiteMap"> </xref> classe para monitorizar o conjunto de <xref href="System.Web.SiteMapProvider"> </xref> objetos que estão disponíveis para o <xref href="System.Web.SiteMap"> </xref> durante a inicialização de mapa de site.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The SiteMapProviderCollection class is a strongly typed <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> collection of <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> objects.
trans-unit.target: A classe de SiteMapProviderCollection é um tipo seguro <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>coleção de <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>objetos.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> </xref:System.Collections.Hashtable>

trans-unit.source: In addition to the two add methods, <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase%29> and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>, the SiteMapProviderCollection class supports the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> method to add an array of type <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Para além das duas adicionar métodos <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase%29>e <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>, a classe de SiteMapProviderCollection suporta o <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A>método para adicionar uma matriz do tipo <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase%29>

trans-unit.source: The SiteMapProviderCollection is used by the <xref:System.Web.SiteMap> class to track the set of <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> objects that are available to the <xref:System.Web.SiteMap> during site map initialization.
trans-unit.target: O SiteMapProviderCollection é utilizado pelo <xref:System.Web.SiteMap>classe para monitorizar o conjunto de <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>objetos que estão disponíveis para o <xref:System.Web.SiteMap>durante a inicialização de mapa de site.</xref:System.Web.SiteMap> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> </xref:System.Web.SiteMap>

trans-unit.source: However, the presence of a <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> in the provider collection does not necessarily mean it is used by a <xref:System.Web.SiteMap> object, only that it is available for use.
trans-unit.target: No entanto, a presença de um <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>no fornecedor de coleção não significam necessariamente que é utilizada por um <xref:System.Web.SiteMap>objeto, apenas que esteja disponível para utilização.</xref:System.Web.SiteMap> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> is stored in the SiteMapProviderCollection, the <xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name%2A> property is used as the key.
trans-unit.target: Quando um <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>é armazenado no SiteMapProviderCollection, o <xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name%2A>propriedade é utilizada como a chave.</xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>

trans-unit.target: O SiteMapProviderCollection o construtor predefinido inicializa quaisquer campos para os respetivos valores predefinidos

trans-unit.target: Adiciona um <xref href="System.Web.SiteMapProvider"> </xref> para a coleção de fornecedor utilizando o <xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name*>propriedade como a chave.</xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name*>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection> object that is returned by the <xref:System.Web.SiteMap.Providers%2A> property is read-only.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection>objeto é devolvido pelo <xref:System.Web.SiteMap.Providers%2A>propriedade é só de leitura.</xref:System.Web.SiteMap.Providers%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection>

trans-unit.source: For this reason, you cannot use the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A> and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> methods to add additional providers programmatically at run time.
trans-unit.target: Por este motivo, não é possível utilizar o <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>e <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A>métodos para adicionar fornecedores adicionais através de programação em tempo de execução.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A> and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> methods are used only in scenarios where you manually create site map provider objects and manage them with an instance of the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Por conseguinte, a <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>e <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A>métodos são utilizados apenas em situações onde manualmente criar objetos do fornecedor de mapa de site e geri-los com uma instância de <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection>classe.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Add method checks the type of the specified provider, and then calls the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29> method to add it to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O método Add verifica o tipo de fornecedor especificado e, em seguida, chama o <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>método para o adicionar à coleção.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>

trans-unit.source: Because the <xref:System.Web.SiteMap> class is static, any <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> contained in its <xref:System.Web.SiteMap.Providers%2A> collection remains for the lifetime of the Web application.
trans-unit.target: Porque o <xref:System.Web.SiteMap>classe é estática, any <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>contidas no respetivo <xref:System.Web.SiteMap.Providers%2A>permanece coleção para a duração da aplicação Web.</xref:System.Web.SiteMap.Providers%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> </xref:System.Web.SiteMap>
